channel.title: +~+~ guild fisher! +!~+~ will pay well!
channel.description:
I am willing to pay well for a flawless guild fisher.
It must be able to fish lobsters, swordfish, and sharks. That's all I need. I suggest making it with the include SRL, since in my opinion it's the best. It must have all the anti randoms possible in SCAR. I need it to be very undetectable, the most undetetable you can get. :) I would love it if it is completely user friendly.(very easy to set up)
IT MUST BE FLAWLESS! Be able to run over night kind of script.
I can't think of anything else right now, but If it meets all my requirements I'll pay up to 2M, maybe higher depending on how flawless it really is.
My MSN is- nightblade09@yahoo.com
